  "key_strengths": [
    "Clear differentiation between reference inaccuracy and claim-overextension — both are checked",
    "Second-hand citation detection is a rare and valuable feature for preventing citation chain inflation",
    "Clarification-first rule when manuscript sections are unavailable prevents overconfident assessments",
    "Scope limitation check (citing papers for claims beyond their actual scope) is a unique safeguard"
  ],
